In the collection of the Senckenberg Deutsches Entomologisches Institut, Müncheberg, 
<collectingCountry box="[1332,1436,367,393]" name="Germany" pageId="23" pageNumber="254">Germany</collectingCountry>
(DEI) it was found a male also collected by Schrottky in the same locality of the 
<typeStatus box="[1051,1157,403,429]" pageId="23" pageNumber="254">lectotype</typeStatus>
. This male is conspecific with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1899" box="[208,332,439,465]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="254" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="proxima">
